				<wikidot:authorName>Buttfranklin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2721810</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Really liked this. Starts out looking like a standalone weird artifact, – enough kooky details that it would stand just as that alone – and then this nice little story just reels itself out all of a sudden. It's not often I'm surprised by the narrative structure of scips these days, so good job. Worldbuilding of Rag Island is a little sparse though – I suppose I'm saying that mainly because it's so intriguing and I want to know more about it.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
